    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enter a world of fear and survival in this thrilling <strong>first-person shooter</strong> and <strong>survival horror game</strong> where your mission is clear: <strong>eradicate a deadly monster</strong> and unravel the mysteries of a haunted, forsaken land. As the tension builds, you'll be forced to scavenge for supplies and fight your way through hostile enemies, all while the lurking terror of a monstrous entity threatens your every step.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279030/extras/93430932749b208077883668230bb271.avif?t=1747056619\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279030/extras_big/93430932749b208077883668230bb271.avif?t=1747056619 width=800 height=432 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survival Horror Gameplay:</strong> Experience heart-pounding tension as you face terrifying enemies and a relentless wendigo.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Open World Exploration:</strong> Uncover hidden mysteries and solve intricate puzzles in a rich, immersive environment.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Weapons and Traps:</strong> Use weapons and traps to tackle and attack the bandits and the dangerous wendigo. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dynamic Monster Encounters:</strong> The wendigo's attacks are sudden and needs you to be super - responsive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279030/extras/58951f47ba88ef5b9bd0feca3cbca787.poster.avif?t=1747056619\" width=750 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279030/extras/58951f47ba88ef5b9bd0feca3cbca787.webm?t=1747056619\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279030/extras/58951f47ba88ef5b9bd0feca3cbca787.mp4?t=1747056619\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Immersive Storytelling:</strong> Unravel the dark history of the place and discover what brought the horror to life.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Time Travel:</strong> A distinctive form of time travel is introduced in a specific segment of the game. </p></li></ul>",
